==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /klVb/

===Noun===
'''club''' (plural [[clubs]])

# a heavy [[stick]] intended for use as a [[weapon]].
# an [[association]] of [[member]]s joining together for some common purpose, especially [[sports]] or [[recreation]].
# a [[nightclub]]
# a [[playing card]] marked with the symbol &clubs;

